data.description: Just reduced, Welcome to your dream home! This immaculate 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom house, 2 car garage and a covered lanai built in 2021, is the perfect blend of modern elegance and comfort. This property offers the ideal setting for you and your family, Key Features:  1. Modern Design:  This home boasts a contemporary design with clean lines and tasteful finishes.  2. Spacious Living:  Enjoy generous living spaces, including a bright and open living room, perfect for family gatherings.  3. Gourmet Kitchen:  The chef's kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample cabinet space.  4. Tranquil Bedrooms:  Four spacious bedrooms provide plenty of room for your family to grow and guests to stay.  5. Luxurious Bathrooms:  Two beautifully designed bathrooms feature modern fixtures and plenty of storage.  6. Energy Efficiency:  Built in 2021, this home comes with energy-efficient features to keep your utility bills in check.  7. Outdoor Oasis:  Step outside to a well-maintained backyard, perfect for outdoor activities and relaxation.  8. Convenient Location:  This home is conveniently located near schools, parks, shopping centers, and major commuter routes.  9. Move-In Ready:  With its pristine condition, this home is move-in ready, so you can start creating memories right away.  10. Garage:  A spacious garage provides secure parking and extra storage space.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning 2021-built home yours! Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the beauty and comfort it has to offer. Your dream home awaits!
